{
  "texts": [
    "Initially, the central server initializes a sequential model M 0 and then deploys it on clients' devices.",
    "Subsequently, clients and the central server collaboratively execute the following steps until model convergence.",
    "At the start of round рқ‘ҹ, the central server selects a group of users U рқ‘ҹ to participate in the training process and distributes recommendation model M рқ‘ҹ to them.",
    "Then, each user рқ‘ў рқ‘– вҲҲ U рқ‘ҹ trains M рқ‘ҹ with their interaction log S рқ‘ў рқ‘– using a specific objective function L рқ‘ҹрқ‘’рқ‘җ, such as binary cross entropy loss:L рқ‘ҹрқ‘’рқ‘җ = - вҲ‘пёҒ рқ‘Ј рқ‘Ў вҲҲ S рқ‘ў рқ‘– пЈ® пЈҜ пЈҜ пЈҜ пЈҜ пЈ° рқ‘ҷрқ‘ңрқ‘”(рқңҺ (рқ‘ҹ рқ‘Ј рқ‘Ў,рқ‘Ў)) + вҲ‘пёҒ рқ‘Ј рқ‘— вҲүS рқ‘ў рқ‘– рқ‘ҷрқ‘ңрқ‘”(1 -рқңҺ (рқ‘ҹ рқ‘Ј рқ‘—,рқ‘Ў)) пЈ№ пЈә пЈә пЈә пЈә пЈ»(1)whereрқ‘Јрқ‘Ў is the concise version of рқ‘Ј рқ‘ў рқ‘– рқ‘Ў, 0 вүӨ рқ‘ҹ рқ‘Ј,рқ‘Ў вүӨ 1 is the prediction score of item рқ‘Ј at time step рқ‘Ў based on the sequence S рқ‘ў рқ‘–, indicating the preference of рқ‘ў рқ‘– to рқ‘Ј.",
    "After local training, user рқ‘ў рқ‘– uploads the updated model M рқ‘ҹ +1 рқ‘ў рқ‘– back to the central server."
  ]
}